1) Create "product.json" in "Template" Folder 
    - {
        "sections":{
          "main":{
                 "type": "main-product",
                 "settings":{
                   ...
                 }
           }
        },
         "order": [
            "main"
        ]
      }
Note: paste default "main" theme code


2) Create "main-product.liquid" in "Section" Folder
- add assets link 
- assign variables 
- render 'media-gallery'
- For Product Information use "For" Loop
    - use "case, when"
    - render 'product-badges'
    - render 'review'
    - render 'price'
    - render 'buy-buttons'
    - render 'color-swatches'
    - render 'responsive-image'
    - render 'pickup-availability'

- and manual codding 
